{"tid":1512059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷氣軍師主埸] 一齊用Twitter去幫助通過《香港人權及民主法案》","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:05:57.000Z","uid":48912,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5995aa07cb51a8a0eebb3bb175c9ba226b9cc883","tid":1512059,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"又係我，幫是旦哥放野上連登<br />\n個人認同戰線已經燒到去全球<br />\n而家要型成中共包圍網 #ChiNazi<br />\n美國帶頭做就會有其他國家跟<br />\n以下為是旦哥FB貼文<br />\n<br />\n沒有白宮聯署的日子 - Twitter 戰線小貼士 - 請詳閱 - 並廣傳<br />\n<br />\n請各位 Twitter User 準備作戰了。既然白宮聯署網唔知幾時先整好，我哋都唔好依賴，每人都幫手在美國國會議員的 Twitter 度留言，請佢哋復會後盡快通過《香港人權及民主法案》吧。以下內容，請搵個方便自己做事嘅地方 save 低。<br />\n<br />\n1/ Twitter 留言寫法：<br />\n而家有四個寫法畀大家參考，字數上係過到 Twitter 限制的，可以拎去用，但當然你有自己寫法係最好，畀議會感覺先唔會咁機械。<br />\nA/<br />\nPlease help Hong Kong people and pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act. #LiberateHK #FreeHK #hkpolicebrutality #hkprotest<br />\n<br />\nB/<br />\nPlease pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act in order to ensure that all residents of Hong Kong are afforded freedom from arbitrary or unlawful arrest, detention, or imprisonment.<br />\n<br />\nC/<br />\nWe have been on the streets in recent months, fighting for freedom. Those HK politicians who recently visited Washington are looking after Beijing's interest, they do not represent us. By passing the #HK Human Rights and Democracy Act, America will help us achieve our goal.<br />\n<br />\nD/<br />\nPlease pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act and help us. We are entering a somber phase of what must inevitably be a protracted and broadening struggle. We shall defend our home and her status as an &quot;internationalized autonomy&quot; under Sino-British Joint Declaration.<br />\n<br />\n2/ 美國國會議員 Twitter 列表 <br />\n下面條Link係美國國會議員的Twitter list，但要慢慢follow，加得太急會唔畀你加。<br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/u-s-representatives/members\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcspan%2Flists%2Fu-s-representatives%2Fmembers&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ5rbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=2beb1176\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/u-s-representatives/members</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n3/ 圖<br />\n用電話save低，留言時貼埋，讓國會議員對我們的訴求一目了然。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69226171_2379741785426288_1459702780812853248_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkcYPI-k4HIHmPPIihAdeTQ5xhxXDKtc-aZYcHh3HOuH9XGV_jduQJEm0m9ETEQwdQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=0305656c87e62eacb4f1d512d760cb86&amp;oe=5E0FAB11\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69226171_2379741785426288_1459702780812853248_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkcYPI-k4HIHmPPIihAdeTQ5xhxXDKtc-aZYcHh3HOuH9XGV_jduQJEm0m9ETEQwdQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D0305656c87e62eacb4f1d512d760cb86%26oe%3D5E0FAB11&h=b3f8aad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69128823_2379758125424654_1016579039105646592_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQnXY3mcG5--8PacQshOYnhVIYFiQuVUE66WWnc85rcHAzXEq1mU95YOFO7cGwQOEU0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=2ff2a0107794b0a75fe51443bdf7a802&amp;oe=5DC93084\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69128823_2379758125424654_1016579039105646592_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQnXY3mcG5--8PacQshOYnhVIYFiQuVUE66WWnc85rcHAzXEq1mU95YOFO7cGwQOEU0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D2ff2a0107794b0a75fe51443bdf7a802%26oe%3D5DC93084&h=50a379c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69297293_2379758175424649_1340184002857795584_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQmLjH0LGej-qWBN1dUFyRv4u-y11tJQFJwoxkyxUgR6zRVRbCEocDsmkhIc-YWjTt4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=8e422a24676c0154dbb89c9c42212952&amp;oe=5DD78863\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.